        "Object Class": "Keter",
        "Special Containment Procedures": ": Foundation-operated web analysis bot Delta-09 (\"LAUGHSTOP\") is to be kept in constant operation and checked for defects twice a week by a Level-2 staff member familiar with its operation. When functional, the bot will search a wide range of file sharing and video streaming websites for SCP-2030 and remove any manifestations discovered. Finding and isolating SCP-2030's point of origin is considered a Delta-Level priority. Efforts to locate the studio where SCP-2030 is filmed are ongoing. "
