        "Special Containment Procedures": ": SCP-1762-1 is held in a standard containment unit at Site-\u2588\u2588. During the periods when SCP-1762-1 releases SCP-1762-2, video logs are to be recorded for future research. Although instances of SCP-1762-2 have been deemed harmless, they should not be allowed to exit their containment unit. "
