        "Item": "SCP-2980",
        "Object Class": "Safe",
        "Special Containment Procedures": ": SCP-2980 is to be contained in a standard item locker at <a href=\"http://www.scp-wiki.net/secure-facility-dossier-site-81\">Site-81</a>. SCP-2980 may only be removed from storage for testing. "
